    conditional-invariant-code-motion
    switch-rewrites
    function-inlining
    loop-strength-reduction
    interval-analysis
    ivt
    ; can't add the type-analysis rules here yet until we fix the correctness bug
    ; described in https://github.com/egraphs-good/eggcc/issues/292
    ))
